data.title: Numismatics
data.meta_description: Tibet - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document summarizes various Tibetan coins from different periods, including Tangkas and Sho-Srang coins. It provides descriptions of the coins, including metal composition, images on the obverse and reverse, weight ranges, mintage dates, and grading and value information. The coins include issues from the Ga-den palace as well as unofficial coins struck by Nepalese traders in Tibet between 1880-1912.
